data.description: Unmissable opportunity! This beautiful property, built in 2021, features gray 18x18 tiles, 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a 2-car garage. High ceilings, modern French doors, brushed nickel fixtures, and LED lights. Spacious gourmet kitchen with custom gray River Rock wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. Generous-sized master bedroom and impressive bathroom with modern double sinks, garden tub, and separate shower. Energy-efficient with a 15 SEER A/C unit, double-pane windows, high-quality shingles, and R38 insulation. Covered rear lanai, fully fenced backyard. Irrigation and in-wall  pest control system included. Finished garage with coach lights and attic access. Centrally located community with pool and recreational areas. Close to shops, restaurants, golf courses, Winter Haven and Orlando attractions. Easy access to main roads. Don't wait, this opportunity won't last!
